New Suggestions view! Recollect has always provided suggestions in the form of photos and prompts. While we were happy with the functionality they provided we realized that the suggestions view was confusing for many people. With the new design it s easier than ever to write in your journal. Scroll through your best photos and videos and prompts. This is only the beginning for Suggestions in Recollect! Also: Updates to the purchases screen.
